    <releaseNotes>
### Added
- Add code style configuration
- Add modpack version in the name for FTB legacy packs
- [Windows] Add desktop shortcut in the installer

### Changed
- Clarify T&C for API keys
- Improve download speed when using the CurseForge API
- Improve whitelisted hosts filtering code
- Make JVM arguments text-field multi-line
- Remove CurseForge API workaround on modpacks
- Show metaserver URL instead of `(default)`
- Update Nix support
- Warn the user of non-whitelisted hosts in mrpacks
- [macOS] Switch background of icon to white

### Fixed
- Correctly handle ATL packs when `mainClass` has a `depends` field
- Fix crash when aborting instance import
- Fix icon importing when using non-standard icon paths
- Fix missing mnemonics in the API page
- Fix modpack's type inference when importing
- Fix search filters for Modrinth
- Properly fix CurseForge modpack installation
- Silence unimportant build warnings
- [Linux] Add missing image-format libraries for the AppImage
- [Linux] Fix image sizes in Flathub
- [Windows] Correctly set PolyMC's version for binaries

### Removed
- [Windows] Remove explicit Vista support

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/PolyMC/PolyMC/compare/1.3.0...1.3.1
